OL,3,CPolice hunt arsonist after car fire
OL,4,Cspreads to house 'where children slept'
OL,6,FPolice in Bristol are hunting an
OL,7,Farsonist after a car fire spread to a
OL,8,Fhouse nearby where three children
OL,9,Fslept.
OL,11,FAvon and Somerset officers are
OL,12,Fappealing for witnesses, information
OL,13,For dashcam footage following the fire
OL,14,Fon Oldbury Court Road in Fishponds.
OL,16,FThey said emergency services were
OL,17,Fcalled to the scene at around 3.20am
OL,18,Fon Saturday 30 August. The home has
OL,19,Fbeen destroyed by the blaze.
