OL,3,CPolice hunt arsonist after car fire
OL,4,Cspreads to house 'where children slept'
OL,6,FWhile fire investigation has yet to be
OL,7,Fcompleted, police are investigating
OL,8,Fthe fire as arson. A car caught fire
OL,9,Fand the blaze spread to the house.
OL,11,FFire investigators and crime scene
OL,12,Finvestigators are also carrying out
OL,13,Fenquiries in the area.
OL,15,FDetective Sergeant Jeremy Cowburn
OL,16,Fsaid: "There were three young children
OL,17,Fin the house at the time of the fire.
OL,18,FIt doesn't bear thinking about what
OL,19,Fcould have happened, but thankfully
OL,20,Feveryone is safe, although the family
OL,21,Fhome is uninhabitable.
